video_title: 👉The Most Important Video You Will See Today❗️ #shorts
transcript:
imagine this is you and this is the
stress that you face every day
stress is inevitable it pours in but you
have the capacity to deal with it for a
while now as that pressure builds you
think you can just keep going but what
if that stress keeps on coming and we
don't do anything about it everyone has
a breaking point
so what's the answer
exercise is your release valve it's free
and it's one of the most powerful things
you can do for your mental health
